snippet.title: Bigg Boss Triumph : @ElvishYadavVlogs's Comic Chronicles!
snippet.description:
Step into the captivating world of a true entertainer, Elvish Yadav – a well-known Indian Youtuber and winner of Bigg Boss OTT Season 2 . This podcast is your express ticket to Elvish's journey, from his YouTube adventures to the thrill of winning Bigg Boss OTT, all while cherishing the unique connection with his supportive fanbase. It's a brief yet lively chat, giving you a glimpse into the life of a vibrant personality, filled with stories, achievements, and the warmth of a dedicated community. Tune in for a dose of entertainment and insights into the dynamic world of Elvish Yadav!

#bhartisingh #elvishyadav #harshlimbachiya #podcast

snippet.title: 100 Million - DIVINE, Karan Aujla | Official Music Video
snippet.description:
Download & Stream: https://lnk.to/100M

'100 Million' is an ode to the unparalleled success achieved by DIVINE and Karan Aujla. This track not only celebrates their achievements but also stands as an anthem, for those with grand dreams. As they savour the fruits of their labour, the artists reflect on the enduring habits that propelled them to the pinnacle. Fueled by explosive bars and bravado, this track marks the inception of a collaborative project between the two industry titans.

snippet.title: Choodu Nanna - Video Song | Yatra 2 | Mammootty | Jiiva | Mahi V Raghav | Santhosh Narayanan
snippet.description:
For more latest songs & videos, subscribe 👉 https://bit.ly/Saregama_Telugu

Presenting the first single "Choodu Nanna" from 'Yatra 2' starring Mammootty, Jiiva & others. Directed by Mahi V Raghav, Music Composed by Santhosh Narayanan.

Song Credits:-
Lyrics : Bhaskarabhatla Ravi Kumar
Singers : Vijaynarain
Composed, Arranged and Programmed by Santhosh Narayanan
Additional Vocals : Santhosh Narayanan
Recorded by Santhosh Narayanan, Rupendar Venkatesh
Recorded at Future Tense Studios -  Chennai
Recording Engineer : Rupendar Venkatesh
Studio Assist : Jaba Raj
Mixed and Mastered by Santhosh Narayanan at Future Tense Studios
Musicians Coordinator : Meenakshi Santhosh

Movie Credits:-
Written & Directed by: Mahi V Raghav
Producer: Shiva Meka
Banners: Three Autumn Leaves, V Celluloid
Music Director: Santhosh Narayanan
DOP : Madhie
Editor : Shravan Katikaneni
Art Director: Selva Kumar
Cast :
Mammootty, Jiiva, Ketaki Narayan, Suzanne Bernert, Mahesh Manjrekar

Lyrics:-
Pallavi:
Choodu Naannaa...Choosthunnaavaa naannaa.. Needa leni nena veella dheema
yemitii enthatiii premaa.. 
Naa dhareto thochakunte 
 Nii vembadae memu antuu
Kadilaaru ento aa nammakam
Nenelaa odduku  cheradam...  Veellanelaa  odduku cherchadam

Charanam 1:
Inti peddhaa.. Kanumoosthey ainavaallu anadhale kadha. 
Nuvvu lekaa.. Prathi ooruu ooruu anadha avvadam yendayyaa..
  Nuvvu lekaa..... Nuvvu lekaa..... Nuvvu lekaa...
Idhi yenaaduu.. Jarigundadhayyaa.. Oo pedayya.. 
Indhari kannulu chimme kanniitinanthaa..
Thudavaalani vundhi kodukuga
Anduku avasaramaiyyee kondantha dhairyam naakivvu..

Charanam 2:
enthala abhimaaname kuripisthunnaro ee janam Anduke ee janmalo teerchesukuntaa ee runam Gadapaki prathi gadapaki nenavuthaa raksha thoranam  Maatapai untaanani chesthunnaa tholi santhakam
Needa leni nena veella dheema...
Choodu naannaa.. Choodu naannaa..
 Choodu naannaa.. Choodu naannaa..
 Choodu naannaa.. Choodu naannaa..
     Choodu naannaa.. Choodu naannaa..

snippet.title: VEG THALI | 15 Varieties of Veg Recipes | Huge South Indian Veg Thali Recipes Cooking In Village
snippet.description:
Today, in our village, we cook 15 varieties of vegetarian recipes for the special Tamil day of the Pongal festival. We cook South Indian Veg thali recipes by cooking the following recipes: Rice, Sambar, Rasam, Mor, Payasam, Appalam, Vadai, Sweet Pongal, Potato fry, Lady Finger masala, Brinjal Masial, Raw banana Fry, Cabbage, Thandu Keerai Masiyal, and Pickle.

The taste is savory!

snippet.title: Exclusive Look Of The Newly Built Ram Mandir & Ayodhya Airport | I Love My India | Curly Tales
snippet.description:
Curly Tales has exclusive access to the newly built Ram Mandir &  Maharishi Valmiki Airport just before the launch. 
The Ram Mandir, set to be inaugurated on January 22nd, has preparations going on in full swing as around 4000 laborers are working on it around the clock. 
The temple is a testament to architectural marvel, constructed without the use of metal or concrete. Instead, a special rock imported from the Bansi Mountain in Rajasthan has been employed.
Along with that get a glimpse of Ayodhya’s four transformed lanes which are the - Bhaktipath, Janma Bhoomi Path, Ram Path & Dharma Path which are reconstructed on the basis of 4 vedas. 
You will also be amazed to see a new systematic way of Darshan for better crowd management that has been arranged by the government. 
Additionally, we give you an exclusive look at the Maharishi Valmiki International Airport, set to launch soon after being constructed in a record time of just 20 months. Inspired by the new Ram Mandir, the airport's walls are adorned with paintings depicting stories from the Ramayana. With the capacity to host about 10 lakh passengers annually, this airport is a remarkable addition to Ayodhya's infrastructure. 
So what are you waiting for,  book your tickets now as various modes of transportation have now been made available to visit Ram Lala.    

#ayodhya #rammandirayodhya #curlytales #foodandtravel #ayodhyadham #ayodhyarammandir #ayodhyatemple #rammandir

00:10 - Introduction

Along with that get a glimpse of Ayodhya’s four transformed lanes which are the - Bhaktipath, Janma Bhoomi Path, Ram Path & Dharma Path which are reconstructed on the basis of 4 vedas. 
You will also be amazed to see a new systematic way of Darshan for better crowd management that has been arranged by the government. 
Additionally, we give you an exclusive look at the Maharishi Valmiki International Airport, set to launch soon after being constructed in a record time of just 20 months. Inspired by the new Ram Mandir, the airport's walls are adorned with paintings depicting stories from the Ramayana. With the capacity to host about 10 lakh passengers annually, this airport is a remarkable addition to Ayodhya's infrastructure. 
So what are you waiting for,  book your tickets now as various modes of transportation have now been made available to visit Ram Lala.

Synopsis:
Militant activities are going out of control in the Srinagar Valley, so a new and elite unit, Air Dragons, is commissioned by the Air Headquarters. They are now the first responders to any hostile activity. They comprise of the best combat aviators handpicked from across the IAF. FIGHTER is the story of Air Dragons who are willing to give it their all for the nation while going through the highs and lows of their internal and external battles.

snippet.description:

snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3984: Sher Ko Kara Repair
--------------------------------------------------------
Sodhi announces his plan to get his car repaired, prompting Roshan to playfully remind him of the troubles it caused. Jethalal suggests getting a new car, but Sodhi opts to repair the existing one. Later, Sodhi has to drop Roshan at her relative's place and Tapu asks him if he can drop Tapu Sena to the mall.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3984, 18 Jan 2024
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: 2nd T20I | Sri Lanka vs Zimbabwe | Highlights | 16th January 2024
snippet.description:

Click here to watch all highlights: https://bit.ly/3OVl9LM

Click here to watch more: https://www.sonyliv.com/sports/cricket-zimbabwe-tour-of-sri-lanka-1700001364

Click here to subscribe now: https://bit.ly/3Q78rHU

Zimbabwe won the toss and decided to bowl first in the 2nd T20I. Sri Lanka lost their top three batters for one-digit scores but later Charith Asalanka and Angelo Mathews stitched up a brilliant partnership. Sri Lanka ended with a total of 173 runs and Zimbabwe then came into bat. Opener Craig Ervine played a superb knock worth 70 runs while Luke Jongwe and Clive Madande's heroics ultimately took Zimbabwe to a thrilling four-wicket victory.

snippet.title: कैसे अपनी ज़िंदगी को बेहतर बनाएँ | Dr Vikas Divyakirti | Drishti IAS @vikasdivyakirti
snippet.description:
प्रिय व्यूअर्स,

अक्सर ही ऐसा होता है कि जिसे एक समय हम जीवन की सफलता मान बैठते हैं, समय के साथ वह केवल एक पड़ाव की तरह लगने लगता है। और सफलता हमें वह संतोष नहीं दे पाती है, जिसके अपेक्षा हम कर रहे होते हैं। इसलिये अपने जीवन में हमें 'सफलता' के साथ-साथ 'सार्थकता' की भी खोज करनी चाहिये। 

इस छोटी सी चर्चा में डॉ. विकास दिव्यकीर्ति सर द्वारा इसी द्वंद्व को समझाने की कोशिश की गई है। सांसारिक सफलताओं के साथ-साथ आत्मिक उन्नति को कैसे साधा जा सकता है, इसका सूत्र भी आपको इस चर्चा में मिलेगा। 

उम्मीद है इससे आपको अपनी ज़िंदगी बेहतर बनाने में मदद मिलेगी। 

शुभकामनाओं सहित, 
टीम दृष्टि

snippet.title: बाजरा की फूली फूली इडली-पोषण से भरपूर-सर्दियों के लिये खास नाश्ता-Nutrient-Rich Millet Idli Recipe
snippet.description:
बाजरे की न्यूट्रीएन्ट पैक्ड-ग्लूटन फ्री इडली, Healthy Bajra Idli Recipe, Wholesome Breakfast,Bajra Flour Recipes,Nutrient-packed Bajra Idli Recipe
#millet #bajrarecipe #winterspecial #idli 

𝐈𝐧𝐠𝐫𝐞𝐝𝐢𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐬 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐁𝐚𝐣𝐫𝐚 𝐈𝐝𝐥𝐢
बाजरा आटा - Pearl millet flour - 1 cup (140 grams)
सूजी - Semolina - 1/4 cup (50 grams)
दही - Curd - 3/4 cup
नमक - Salt - 1 tsp
हरी मिर्च - Green chilli - 1 tsp, chopped
अदरक - Ginger - 1 tsp, grated
हरे मटर - Green peas - 1/2 cup
इनो फ्रुट सॉल्ट - Eno fruit salt - 1 tsp
 
𝐅𝐨𝐫 𝐂𝐡𝐮𝐭𝐧𝐞𝐲
मूंगफली - Peanuts - 1/2 cup
नारियल - Coconut - 1/2 cup, grated
नमक - Salt - 1/2 tsp
हरी मिर्च - Green chilli - 2 no
अदरक - Ginger - 1 inch
नींबू का रस - Lemon juice - 2 tsp
तेल - Oil - 3 tbsp
सरसों के दाने - Mustard seeds - 1 tsp
उरद दाल - Urad dal - 1 tsp
लाल मिर्च - Red chilli - 2 no
करी पत्ता - Curry leaves - 20-25 no

snippet.title: यह लोकतंत्र नहीं, धर्मतंत्र है
snippet.description:
लोकतंत्र की जगह धर्मतंत्र ने ली है। इस धर्मतंत्र के सामने भारत के लोकतंत्र की तस्वीर धुंधली होती जा रही है बल्कि धर्मतंत्र इतना हावी हो चुका है कि इसके बग़ैर आज के भारत में आप लोकतंत्र देख भी नहीं सकते हैं। धर्म तंत्र का मतलब ही ऐसा हो गया है कि पार्टियां धार्मिक आयोजन कराने वाली संस्था में बदलती जा रही हैं। पहले धर्म से दूरी बनाकर रखती थीं मगर अब पार्टियां राजनीति से ही दूरी बनाने लगी हैं। पूंजी के दबाव में राजनीतिक दलों के भीतर राजनीति खत्म हुई और अब धर्म का नाम लेकर लोकतंत्र के मैदान से ही राजनीतिक दल खत्म हो रहे हैं। अगर लोकतांत्रिक चरित्र पर धार्मिक चरित्र हावी हुआ तो वह लोकतंत्र को नौटंकी में बदल देगा। एक दिन धर्म भी नौटंकी की तरह नज़र आने लगेगा।मेरी इस बात को लिख कर पर्स में रख लीजिए

https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC0yXUUIaPVAqZLgRjvtMftw/join

snippet.description:
Ayodhya Ram Mandir: 22 जनवरी से पहले कोई गड़बड़ मत करना... वरना योगी जी हैं ना ! Ground Report

snippet.title: Coaching Centre: 16 साल से कम उम्र के बच्चों की Coaching बंद, आदेश नहीं मानने पर 1 लाख का जुर्माना
snippet.description:
Coaching Centre Banned For Students Under 16 Years: शिक्षा मंत्रालय द्वारा घोषित नए दिशानिर्देश के मुताबिक कोचिंग संस्थान 16 साल से कम उम्र के विद्यार्थियों को अपने यहां दाखिल नहीं कर सकेंगे और अच्छे नंबर या रैंक दिलाने की गारंटी जैसे भ्रामक वादे भी नहीं कर सकेंगे. कोचिंग संस्थानों को विनियमित करने के लिए दिशानिर्देश एक कानूनी ढांचे की आवश्यकता को पूरा करने और बेतरतीब तरीके से निजी कोचिंग संस्थानों की बढ़ोतरी को रोकने के लिए हैं. मंत्रालय ने यह दिशानिर्देश विद्यार्थियों की आत्महत्या के बढ़ते मामलों, आग की घटनाओं, कोचिंग संस्थानों में सुविधाओं की कमी के साथ-साथ उनके द्वारा अपनाई जाने वाली शिक्षण पद्धतियों के बारे में सरकार को मिली शिकायतों के बाद तैयार किए हैं.

snippet.title: पेड़ को देखकर डर गए Jetha और Bapuji | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Revisit The Journey
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBIT1FSJW6yTlzqK-31FDWg?sub_confirmation=1

All the ladies of the Gokuldham Society are scared of the ghost. But the men refuse to believe it. The men decide to guard society at night to prove that there are no ghosts. Daya, according to her mother's advice, plans to send Jethalal to perform the task of getting rid of the ghost. 

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 418
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2023 #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #jethalal #tarakmehta 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

snippet.title: "പേടിയായിരുന്നു പുറത്തിറങ്ങാൻ പോലും" | @ajuwithami6281 | Josh Talks Malayalam
snippet.description:
#joshtalksmalayalam #ajuwithami #contentcreator 
പഠിച്ചുകൊണ്ട് വളരൂ ജോഷ് Talks-ലൂടെ- നിങ്ങളുടെ Communication Skills മെച്ചപ്പെടുത്താൻ, ജോഷ് ടോക്സിന്റെ Malayalam to English app-ൽ ചേരുക: ‌https://joshskills.app.link/QRSpMrLudGb

ഒരു ശ്രമവും ചെറിയ പ്രയത്നമല്ല. നിറയേ സ്വപ്നങ്ങളും സ്വപ്നങ്ങൾ എങ്ങനെ നിറവേറ്റണം എന്ന ആശയക്കുഴപ്പവും മാത്രമുള്ള ഒരു പെൺകുട്ടി എന്ന നിലയിൽ നിന്ന്, @ajuwithami6281  എന്ന #youtubechannel -ലെ  ആമി എന്ന പേരിൽ പ്രേക്ഷകർക്ക് പരിചിതയായ ആമിന, തന്റെ അഭിനിവേശം പിന്തുടരാൻ എന്തെല്ലാം #challenges  നേരിട്ടു എന്നാണ് തന്റെ #joshtalks -ലൂടെ നമ്മോട് പറയുന്നു. ഇന്ന് #8lakhs -ൽ അധികം  #subscribers  ഉള്ള തങ്ങളുടെ #channel  , ആമിനയും ഭർത്താവും ഒരുമിച്ച് അവരുടെ താൽപ്പര്യമേഖലയിൽ എല്ലാ നിഷേധാത്മകതയ്ക്കും ശേഷം വിജയിക്കുന്നു. സോഷ്യൽ മീഡിയയിൽ സജീവമായിരിക്കുമ്പോൾ താൻ നേരിട്ട #bodyshaming -നെയും ഒരാളുടെ ആത്മവിശ്വാസം കെടുത്താൻ ആളുകൾ എന്തെല്ലാം പറയും എന്നും ആമിന അഭിസംബോധന ചെയ്യുന്നു.

No effort is a small effort. From being merely a girl with dreams and confusions on how to fulfill her dreams, Amina, known to her audience as Ami from @ajuwithami6281  tells us through her #joshtalks on how it for her was to #challenge  the community to follow her #passion . With now more than #8lakh #subscribers  today, Amina along with her husband together are going #successful  in their area of interest after all the negativities being thrown at them. Amina also addresses the #bodyshaming she faced while being active in #socialmedia and the extends to which people go to tarnish one's confidence.

ഇപ്പോൾ നിങ്ങൾക്ക് Josh Talks വീഡിയോകളിൽ നിങ്ങളുടെ ബ്രാൻഡ് പ്രദർശിപ്പിക്കാനും പരസ്യം ചെയ്യാനും varun@joshtalks.com- ഇൽ Connect ചെയ്യൂ.

If you find this talk helpful, please like and share it and let us know in the comments box.
You can now showcase and advertise your brand on the Josh Talks videos, reach out to us at varun@joshtalks.com, if you are interested.

Josh Talks passionately believes that a well-told story has the power to reshape attitudes, lives, and ultimately, the world. We are on a mission to find and showcase the best motivational stories from across India through documented videos and live events held all over the country. Josh Talks Malayalam caters to the Malayalam speaking audience worldwide. It aims to inspire and motivate Malayali's by showcasing Malayalam motivation through the experiences of fellow Malayali's. Josh talks Malayalam and brings to you the best Malayalam motivational videos. What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags to riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, women’s rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. With 9 languages in our ambit, our stories and speakers echo one desire: to inspire action. Our goal is to unlock the potential of passionate young Indians from rural and urban areas by inspiring them to overcome the setbacks they face in their career and helping them discover their true calling in life.

ജോഷ് Talks ഇന്ത്യയിലെ ഏറ്റവും പ്രേരണാത്മകമായ കഥകൾ ശേഖരിക്കുകയും അവ പങ്കുവെക്കാൻ ഒരു വേദി നൽകുകയും ചെയ്യുന്നു. വിവിധ പശ്ചാത്തലങ്ങളിൽ നിന്നുള്ള അനുഭവസ്ഥർ, അവരുടെ സംഘർഷഭരിത കഥകൾ പങ്കുവയ്ക്കുന്നു. ചെറുതായി തുടങ്ങിയ ജോഷ് Talks, നിലവിൽ 9 ഭാഷകളിൽ കഥകൾ പങ്കുവയ്ക്കുന്നു. ഊർജ്ജസ്വലരായ യുവജനങ്ങളുടെ കഴിവുകളെ പ്രോത്സാഹിപ്പിക്കുകയും, അവരുടെ ജീവിതത്തിൽ  നേരിടുന്ന തിരിച്ചടികൾ മറികടക്കാൻ അവർക്ക് പ്രചോദനം നൽകുകയും ചെയ്യുക എന്നതാണ് ഞങ്ങളുടെ ലക്ഷ്യം.
#familyvlog #joshtalks #bodyshaming #vlogger
